com.cyc.session

Interface SessionManagerConfigurationProperties


  • public interface SessionManagerConfigurationProperties
    This defines the canonical set of names for all SessionManagerConfiguration properties. Although some implementations of the SessionManagerConfiguration interface may not require these keys, they should be used in any implementation backed by Properties or any form of map with String-based keys.
